snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP vs. Amber Heard 🥊 Psychic Truth Check ✅ Who is a liar, and who was the aggressor? 🔮
snippet.description:
TODAY, we talk about the infamous divorce and libel case between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard to discover who is lying, who is telling the truth, and who was the true aggressor and abuser. The answer may shock you. It did me!

Please note: I intended for this to be a shorter reading which is why I mentioned this in the video. I'm finding these will be "healthier" lengths in order to capture all the information that's offered. 

🗣️ Welcome to PSYCHIC TRUE CRIME where we dive into the psychology of known and unknown killers, criminals, and celebrities and aim to bring greater awareness to unsolved crimes and crimes that left an imprint on history using intuition and psychic readings.
